# Future Work

- Add authentication so players can track progress across sessions
- Improve error handling for API requests to the cloud database
- Add additional player statistics (wins, losses, deck composition)
- Explore moving to a full SQL or NoSQL cloud solution for scalability
- Implement real-time multiplayer using the cloud database for state synchronization

